     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet IMMZD2DTMalariaVS</b></p><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMalariaVS\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZD2DTMalariaVS\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 12 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMalariaVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20less|20than|205|20months-41\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageislessthan5months-41\">Client's age is less than 5 months-41</a></td><td>Client's age is less than 5 months</td><td><div><p>Today's date − \"Date of birth\" &lt; 5 months</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMalariaVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20not|20due|20for|20malaria|20vaccination-48\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Clientisnotdueformalariavaccination-48\">Client is not due for malaria vaccination-48</a></td><td>Client is not due for malaria vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Not due\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMalariaVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20malaria|20primary|20series|20doses|20were|20administered-116\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Nomalariaprimaryseriesdoseswereadministered-116\">No malaria primary series doses were administered-116</a></td><td>No malaria primary series doses were administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Malaria vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 0</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMalariaVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20more|20than|20or|20equal|20to|205|20months-41\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageismorethanorequalto5months-41\">Client's age is more than or equal to 5 months-41</a></td><td>Client's age is more than or equal to 5 months</td><td><div><p>Today's date − \"Date of birth\" ≥ 5 months</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMalariaVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20due|20for|20malaria|20vaccination-44\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Clientisdueformalariavaccination-44\">Client is due for malaria vaccination-44</a></td><td>Client is due for malaria vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Due\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMalariaVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-One|20malaria|20primary|20series|20dose|20was|20administered-116\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Onemalariaprimaryseriesdosewasadministered-116\">One malaria primary series dose was administered-116</a></td><td>One malaria primary series dose was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Malaria vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 1</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMalariaVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-The|20latest|20malaria|20dose|20was|20administered|20less|20than|204|20weeks|20ago-99\"> </a><code>http://smart.wh